    dc:description "Figure 7. Dorylaimellus paracrassidens sp. nov. (A) Entire female, (B) anterior region, (C) anterior end showing amphid, (D) pharyngeal region, (E) expanded part of pharynx, (F) female genital system, (G) female posterior region." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5209789/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5209791>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Dorylaimellus paracrassidens sp. nov. (A) Anterior region, (B) anterior end showing amphid, (C) expanded part of pharynx, (D) vulval region, (E) vulval region in ventral view, (F) female posterior end. (Scale bars: A, B = 10 µm; C–F = 20 µm.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5209791/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

